{"tid":687112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發現呢一套戲都犯左法，警犬快啲拉人","createTime":"2018-06-02T02:53:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T03:32:36.000Z","uid":19527,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ae700f3ca01c09745dc86f1c552e67d6cb84b3bb","tid":687112,"uid":19527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T02:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/105203_7001d3e024af75ed6e50a654583728fa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F105203_7001d3e024af75ed6e50a654583728fa.png&h=bf4d7b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《中華人民共和國刑法》第三百七十二條規定，冒充軍人招搖撞騙罪是指以謀取非法利益為目的，冒充軍人招搖撞騙的行為。具體表現形式多種多樣，如穿戴軍人服飾行騙，使用偽造的軍人證件行騙，等等。"},{"pid":"45e2704f7b2f4876dd0bf8ae04ab03505a1ab8af","tid":687112,"uid":157362,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:19:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8cd50d5e46554ab65bc4f4dfc06d8c011605280a","tid":687112,"uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T03:32:36.000Z","msg":"真膠定假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}